snippet.title: FIFA 14 - Wii Gameplay (4K60fps)
snippet.description:
FIFA 14 - Wii Gameplay (4K60fps).

FIFA 14 is a football simulation video game developed by EA Canada and published by Electronic Arts worldwide under the EA Sports label. It was released in September 2013 for the PlayStation 2, PlayStation 3, PlayStation Portable, PlayStation Vita, Xbox 360, Wii, Nintendo 3DS and Microsoft Windows.
